            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Shred apart the <strong>duck</strong> using two forks (watch out for any bones!) – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat and add the <strong>reserved duck jelly </strong>and the <strong>pulled duck</strong></p><p>Mix together until fully combined and warmed through – this is your <strong>pulled confit duck</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1657624269664-x200.jpg",
